import React from 'react'

    Flex,

    FormControl,
    Box,
    InputGroup,
    Icon,
    Grid,
    GridItem,
    FormLabel,
    Progress,
    Input,
    Textarea
} from "@chakra-ui/react";
import { Checkbox, CheckboxGroup } from "@chakra-ui/react";
import { useHistory } from "react-router-dom";
const history=useHistory()
const Welcome = () => {
    const onClick=()=>{
        
    }

        <Flex minHeight="100vh" fontFamily="Roboto"  bg="#F9F9F9" direction="column" justify="center" align="center">

              </Button>
              <Text fontSize="12px" lineHeight="18px" color="#525252" mb="16px">
                    OR
              </Text>

                  Sign up with Apple
              </Button>
              <Button mb="200px" borderRadius="22px" color="#F9F9F9" height="44px" w="100%" fontSize="16px"  bg="#949494" py="6.5px" >
                  Sign up with Facebook
              </Button>
              <Box w="137px"  mb="9px" height="5px" bg="black" borderRadius="100px">

export default Welcome
